/// Material Design Icons depicting **the physical world and everything in it**.
/// Contains all World SVG paths, which can be retrieved by calling {@link #path()} or {@link #toString()}.
///
/// This category captures tangible objects, living beings, places, and activities:
///
/// - **Nature & Weather** — trees, flowers, sun, moon, lightning, water, seasons
/// - **People** — faces, body parts, gestures, family, professions
/// - **Animals** — mammals, birds, fish, insects, fantasy creatures
/// - **Places & Buildings** — maps, cities, churches, factories, airports, bridges
/// - **Transport & Vehicles** — cars, trains, planes, boats, fuel, traffic
/// - **Sports & Games** — balls, trophies, board games, outdoor activities
/// - **Home & Furniture** — beds, appliances, lighting, HVAC, windows
/// - **Tools & Equipment** — wrenches, hammers, saws, lab equipment, heavy machinery
/// - **Food & Drink** — meals, beverages, ingredients, kitchen items
/// - **Commerce & Finance** — cash, cards, carts, stores, banking
/// - **Clothing & Accessories** — shoes, hats, glasses, jewelry
/// - **Weapons** — swords, ammunition, bows, firearms
/// - **Medical** — pills, syringes, stethoscopes, viruses, bandages
/// - **Religious & Cultural** — crosses, menorahs, meditation, peace symbols
